      <textAnnotation id="sid-B94210FA-59BE-4FCA-8197-672F6BB96C96" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Stock will be bailed by Intel Product by agreed bailment process (107/109 Movement type) to Intel Foundry facility directly which needs to consume that stock to produce next stage material/FG.
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
